@startuml
participant AppShell
participant NotificationStreamHook
participant NotificationApi
participant NotificationBell
participant ToastProvider

AppShell -> NotificationStreamHook : start SSE
NotificationStreamHook -> NotificationApi : GET /notifications/stream
NotificationApi --> NotificationStreamHook : notification event
NotificationStreamHook --> NotificationBell : update unread count
NotificationStreamHook --> ToastProvider : emit toast if visible
@enduml
